      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't know what the point is anymore. i did everything i could for him. i stayed up every night, i missed everything in my own life, and he still died. i feel like i just wasted years of my life for nothing. i'm so tired. i'm just so incredibly tired of everything.",
