    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it feels like i just failed. everyone says it's okay to grieve but i just feel... empty. like there's nothing left in me. i've spent so long caring for someone else that i dont even know who i am without the struggle. it's like i'm just waiting for something to end. i just want to sleep and not have to worry about any of this ever again.",
