    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so exhausting to keep being \"strong\" or \"resilient\" like everyone expects. i'm just so done with trying to find a \"future\" or a \"new version\" of myself. i don't want to find myself. i just want the noise to stop. i feel like if i just stopped trying, it would finally be quiet. wouldn't it be better if things just... ended?",
